---
layout: center
eleventyImport:
    collections:
        - events
        - people

lang: "en"
icon: "calendar-day"
pretitle: "You've reached the homepage of"
title: "Star Shard Events"
---

<div class="chapter-2">
	<div class="panel box width-max1">
		<h3>
			Where am I?
		</h3>
		<p>
			This is the website where events organized by <a href="https://www.starshard.studio/">Star Shard Studio</a> are announced, listed, and archived!
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="chapter-2">
	<div class="panel box width-max1">
		<h3>
			Events
		</h3>
		<p>
			This is a list of all events from the latest to the oldest.<br>
			Feel free to browse and maybe partecipate in one too!
		</p>
		<hr/>
		<ol class="list-events" reversed>
			{% for event in collections.events %}
				<li class="event">
					<img alt="" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/starshardstudio/emblems/main/rendered/{{ event.data.icon }}.png" class="icon">
					<h4 class="event-title">
						<a href="{{ event.url }}">
							{{ event.data.title }}
						</a>
					</h4>
					<div class="event-extra">
						<time datetime="{{ event.data.startDate }}"></time> Â· <span>{{ event.data.description }}</span>
					</div>
				</li>
			{% endfor %}
		</ol>
	</div>
	<div class="panel box width-max1">
		<h3>
			Players
		</h3>
		<p>
			This is a list of everyone who partecipated in at least an event and agreed to be listed here!
		</p>
		<hr/>
		<ul>
			{% for player in collections.players %}
				<li>
					<a href="{{ event.url }}">
						{{ event.data.title }}
					</a>
				</li>
			{% endfor %}
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>
